bot.net
Class NetIF

java.lang.Object
  bot.net.NetIF
Direct Known Subclasses:
IOService
public class NetIF
extends java.lang.Object

NetIF is an automatic interface to simplify bot network communications, and it includes facilities to automate creation of services by inheritance.

Author:
Brady O'Brien
See Also:
